<h2>Step 1: Online Application</h2>

<h3>Getting to know you</h3>

<p>Complete our short application form for your chosen role&nbsp;- easy!</p>

<h2>Step 2: Online tests</h2>

<h3>Testing your strengths &amp; abilities</h3>

<p>You will receive two emails to complete our two online tests; our TfL situational strengths test and a combined general ability test. These should take about an hour and must be completed within 7 days.</p>
