<h2>Step 3: Video Interview</h2>
<h3>Revealing your passion</h3>
<p>We want to know about you: what motivates you and why you've applied for the role.</p>
<p>You will be sent an email for a video interview and will have 7 days to complete this. You'll film yourself responding to questions. You can complete this video interview at whatever time suits you - just choose a quiet place.</p>
<p>Don't panic if this is your first video interview, we'll send you an optional practise link beforehand. Watch this video for tips on how to do it:</p>
